                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17931030-71-off377 t17931030-71-cd378"></join>, forty-one yards of fustian, called thickset, value 5 l. sixteen yards of cotton velveteen, value 2 l. twenty yards of velveret for waistcoats, value 2 l. 10 s. fifty yards of woollen cloth, value 18 l. twelve yards of printed dimity, value 24 s. the goods of 
                     
