               <p>(The case opened by Mr. Knapp.)</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17931030-71-person826">
                  WALTER
                   HEBDEN
               <interp inst="t17931030-71-person826" type="surname" value="HEBDEN"></interp>
